#

Grilled Lemon Herb Chicken with Garlic Butter Asparagus

$15
450 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

EasyHealthyQuick

Description

A zesty grilled chicken paired with tender asparagus in a rich garlic butter sauce, bursting with flavor!

Ingredients

  • Chicken breast: 2 pieces
  • Olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • Lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • Garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • Fresh parsley: 2 tablespoons, chopped
  • Dried oregano: 1 teaspoon
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Asparagus: 1 bunch
  • Butter: 2 tablespoons
